<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Pentagon officials acknowledged Tuesday they
are still trying to figure out the effects of a potentially
far-reaching freeze on ``tainted'' contracts announced last week by
Defense Secretary Frank C. Carlucci in the weapons-buying
investigation.
   Defense contractors said they remained in the dark about what
