<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Schwarzenegger Adv15-17   07-05 0903</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Schwarzenegger, Adv 15-17,0922</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv15</NOTE>
